PS10010001.title: Refrigerator Evaporator Fan Motor
PS10010001.description: This evaporator fan motor circulates cool air over the refrigerator's evaporator coils, ensuring even cooling throughout the freezer and fridge compartments.

PS10010002.title: Refrigerator Defrost Thermostat
PS10010002.description: This defrost thermostat regulates the temperature inside your refrigerator's evaporator coil to prevent ice buildup.

PS10010003.title: Refrigerator Water Inlet Valve
PS10010003.description: Controls the flow of water to the ice maker and water dispenser. A failing valve may leak, clog, or stop the ice maker from producing ice.

PS10010004.title: Refrigerator Start Relay
PS10010004.description: The start relay helps the refrigerator compressor start up. A broken relay may cause clicking sounds or prevent cooling entirely.

PS10010005.title: Refrigerator Door Gasket – White
PS10010005.description: This flexible magnetic gasket seals the refrigerator door shut to maintain a consistent interior temperature and improve energy efficiency.

PS10010006.title: Refrigerator Temperature Sensor
PS10010006.description: This thermistor monitors fresh food and freezer temperature and provides feedback to the control board.

PS10010007.title: Refrigerator Ice Maker Assembly
PS10010007.description: A complete replacement ice maker assembly for refrigerators with failed harvest cycles or stuck ejector arms.

PS10010008.title: Refrigerator Condenser Fan Motor
PS10010008.description: Circulates air across the condenser coils to dissipate heat and maintain proper cooling performance.

PS10010009.title: Refrigerator Crisper Drawer
PS10010009.description: This replacement crisper drawer fits many refrigerator models and helps maintain humidity levels for produce.

PS10010010.title: Refrigerator Air Filter
PS10010010.description: A high-efficiency carbon air filter that reduces odors and improves overall air circulation in the refrigerator.

PS20020001.title: Dishwasher Upper Rack Adjuster Kit – Left & Right
PS20020001.description: This kit allows the dishwasher's upper rack to slide smoothly on its track and includes left and right adjusters with wheels.

PS20020002.title: Dishwasher Water Inlet Valve
PS20020002.description: Controls water entry into the dishwasher. A failing valve may leak, restrict flow, or stop the cycle from filling.

PS20020003.title: Dishwasher Heating Element
PS20020003.description: Heats the water and dries dishes. Signs of failure include wet dishes, poor cleaning, or tripped breakers.

PS20020004.title: Dishwasher Spray Arm
PS20020004.description: Rotating spray arm that distributes water through the dishwasher tub to clean dishes effectively.

PS20020005.title: Dishwasher Drain Pump
PS20020005.description: This drain pump expels water from the dishwasher tub and is essential for wash and rinse cycles.

PS20020006.title: Dishwasher Door Gasket
PS20020006.description: Creates a watertight seal around the dishwasher door to prevent leaks during wash cycles.

PS20020007.title: Dishwasher Float Switch
PS20020007.description: Monitors the water level in the tub to prevent overfilling and activates the inlet valve.

PS20020008.title: Dishwasher Detergent Dispenser
PS20020008.description: Releases detergent during the wash cycle. Faulty doors can prevent soap from dispensing properly.

PS20020009.title: Dishwasher Lower Rack Wheel
PS20020009.description: This wheel attaches to the lower dish rack and allows it to roll smoothly on the track.

PS20020010.title: Dishwasher Control Board
PS20020010.description: Manages dishwasher functions such as water level, heating, spray cycles, and display controls.
